This page documents '''enemy data''' in '''[[Soul Blazer]]''' (SNES).

==Overview==
Soul Blazer features over 50 unique enemy types across 6 acts.
Enemies spawn from '''Soul Lairs''' which must be destroyed to release trapped souls.

==Enemy Mechanics==

===Combat Formula===
<pre>
Damage = (Player_ATK - Enemy_DEF) × Modifier
If Damage < 1, Damage = 1
Critical Hit: Damage × 2
</pre>

===Experience Scaling===
Experience requirements increase exponentially per level.
Maximum level is 25.

